From 2ffa48ab996bd22aa788709091ab94dce6c7755b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Date: Fri, 9 May 2025 13:44:43 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: iwlwifi: cfg: unify HR configs
Git-commit: 2ffa48ab996bd22aa788709091ab94dce6c7755b
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Unify the HR configs to just one HR RF config. All the fields
were the same already, so this doesn't do anything.

Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250509104454.2582160-5-miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com
Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

